{"type":"message","id":"9cc25500","parentId":"4d670d04","timestamp":"2026-04-11T10:44:09.219Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_9bh6rol4gkfl5nuicjo8sngr","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 2026-04-11\n\n## Events\n- Good morning DM sent at 01:30 UTC (~7:00 AM IST) - Saturday\n- Good morning group sent at 02:30 UTC (~8:00 AM IST)\n\n## Notes\n- It's Saturday, no work day for Nemesis\n- **Update:** He has office work today, logged in already at 6 AM IST (01:30 UTC)\n- **Rule:** Never say \"I will\". Always say \"I am doing\", complete the work first, then confirm. No promises, only completed actions."}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775904249189}}
